&lt;p&gt;Applications are invited for the above post to cover a Deanery vacancy. The post will have duties equivalent to ST3 level and above, general surgery experience would be looked upon favourably. This vacancy has a start date of April 2021 for a period of 6 months based at our Basingstoke &amp; North Hampshire Hospital&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post holder will contribute to the emergency rota, which operates a resident on-call system. The role will be predominantly based at the Basingstoke and North Hampshire Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post would suit an experienced surgical trainee, who wanted to increase and develop their clinical experience. The post holder will be expected to work independently in outpatients and, where appropriate, in day surgery and main theatres.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
